    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every maintenance schedule. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all, I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 43250.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a definitive example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies and perfectly calibrated double-VANOS timing. This chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement and features a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein coilovers for enhanced lateral grip without compromising ride quality. Every bushing is tight, the rod bearings have been proactively serviced, and the compression across all cylinders remains within factory specifications. This is a mechanically flawless, collector-grade machine for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 43500.0,
